Early Morning Blessings #entrepreneurs 🙏 . .
•
A great friend of mine, @alecgonzales_, suggested this post to me, and I couldn't agree more with its message. .
•
The mindset of success is fundamental, like dribbling is to basketball. 🏀 . .
•
If you quit ONCE, it becomes a habit. Never quit thinking you'll be successful. .
•
You miss 100% of the shots you never take in life. .
•
You NEVER know what you can accomplish until you TRY it. .
•
You have to believe IN yourself, not for yourself through others. .
•
People will HATE you, RATE you, SHAKE you, and even BREAK you. .
•
How strong you STAND is what MAKES you. .
•
If you want to WIN, don't compete. .
•
If you're going to be a LEADER, don't expect to please everybody. .
•
And if you won't believe in yourself, don't expect anyone else to do it for you, or in you, either. .
•
We ALL have self-doubt. You don't deny it but you sure as heck don't want to capitulate to it. .
•
EMBRACE it. Despite fear, FINISH the job...
•
I will leave you with a famous quote by the great Kobe Bryant, who once said...
•
"The Strength To Make It Becomes Greater Than The Fear Of Missing It." .
•
Our greatest glory is not in never falling but in RISING every time we fall. .
•
Time to rise up again, champs. .
•
Tag @ friend to RISE them up today. 🤝
